description.en: $DOGGY is the coin that would allow you to exchange for Crypto Doggy #NFT. These cute animated doggies are designed by one of our featured artists, and will have a gif format. They are programmatically generated, resulting in 10,000 different types of Doggies, with different rarity and collectable value such as common, uncommon and rare.
